p skills that will last your entire career we currently focus on the following areas in our recruitments efforts accountingfinance engineering information technology military veterans at mississippi power we offer rewarding careers and challenging opportunities that leverage your discipline problemsolving skills and leadership abilities professionals  skilled craft we are always looking for skilled professionals to join our team and we offer packages that are extremely competitive hiring process use our online tool to search our openings if you see an opening that interest you or you would like to be notified of future opportunities the first step is to create a candidate profile please include your work experience education and skills along with a recent resume for your profile once youve created a profile you can apply online for jobs that match your qualification you may check your status and update your information at any time sample employment test mississippi power uses preemployment testing as a way to help identify potential candidates for job openings we have a variety of tests which include construction and skill traded selection system cast customer service representative csr plant operator selection system poss power plant maintenance positions selection system mass support and administrative selection system sass technical occupations selection system tech payment options  my home  mississippi power  a southern company my account login not registered sign up now to manage your account online report an outage home my home pay my bill viewreport an outage find an office startstop service contact us overview my bill about my bill billing options paperless billing budget billing other billing options bill alerts payment options authorized payment locations customer unclaimed refund causes of change understanding your meter payment assistance project share liheap programs liheap steps pricing and rates ways to save energy checkup independent service contract