ill find our bill format easy to read your bill — both electronic and paper — also includes a month graph to track your usage view your bill view paper sample sign up for paperless billing receive an email notification each month when your paperless bill is sent and get immediate payment confirmation no more worrying about your check being lost or arriving late in the mail learn more mississippi power co company profile  bloomberg feedback mississippi power co public company company profile sector utilities industry utilities subindustry integrated utilities mississippi power company provides utility services the company generates transmits distributes and sells electricity to residential and commercial uses as well as offers energy conservation services mississippi power serves customers in the state of mississippi corporate information address po box  gulfport ms  united states phone  fax  web url wwwmississippipowercom board members chairman company board members company carl chaney first nbc bank holding co show more from the web key executives g edison holland jr ed chairman anthony wilson presidentceo frances v turnage vpcfotreasurer sponsored financial commentaries more from the web home news top headlines most popular exclusive law entrepreneurs leaders economy environment science sports markets magazine pursuits magazine bloomberg visual data bloomberg best and worst for comments or complaints about news coverage click here regions us china europe asia uk  ireland australia  new zealand canada india  pakistan japan africa eastern europe latin america middle east markets commodities currencies bonds stocks energy markets municipal bonds emerging markets funds islamic finance industries energy technology real estate finance health care transportation insurance retail media manufacturing quick market data stocks stock futures world indexes americas europe middle east  africa asiapacific gainers  losers earnings calendar industry leaders currencies americas eur